Class DefaultOIDCClaimsCallbackHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wso2.carbon.identity.openidconnect.DefaultOIDCClaimsCallbackHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public class DefaultOIDCClaimsCallbackHandler
extends Object
implements CustomClaimsCallbackHandler
    Default implementation of CustomClaimsCallbackHandler. This callback handler populates available user claims after filtering them through requested scopes using OpenIDConnectClaimFilter.
